Azure AI Search Index Design
Recommendation

Create one Azure AI Search index for Phase 0.

Name:

idx-optisweep-phase0-knowledge

Do not create one index per dataset yet. That is overkill for Phase 0.

Instead, include fields that allow filtering by dataset/container.

Indexable Record Types

Only index records useful for retrieval.

Index these:

context reference
incident records
timeline events
workflow definitions
procedure dictionary
raw evidence chunks
escalation summaries

Do not index:

ingestion runs
most source artifact metadata unless description is useful
